     "id": "16840ab7-3020-4b74-86b3-669b0dbebf1e"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* --- Casimir eigenvalues on the output irrep mu, and the Q-polynomial degrees ---\n   Column-ordered generating function (Kazakov et al conventions): G4[u] = Prod_i (u - h(mu_i+4-i)),\n   whose coefficients are the Casimirs. Eigenvalues are symmetric functions of the centered\n   shifted weights xw_i = mu_i + 5/2 - i (= mu_i + rho_i); Pw_k = Sum_i xw_i^k. *)\nClearAll[muhat, xw, Pw, Cas2, Cas4, degQ];\nmuhat[mu_] := Table[mu[[i]] + 4 - i, {i, 4}];\nxw[mu_] := Table[mu[[i]] + 5/2 - i, {i, 4}];\nPw[mu_, k_] := Total[xw[mu]^k];\nCas2[mu_] := Pw[mu, 2] - 5;\nCas4[mu_] := Pw[mu, 4] + 4 Pw[mu, 3] - Pw[mu, 1] Pw[mu, 2] + Pw[mu, 2]/2 - 2 Pw[mu, 1]^2 - 10 Pw[mu, 1] - 51/4;\n(* the SAME shifted weights fix the Q-degrees: deg q_k = (S+P+3) - muhat_k = (S+P) - mu_k + (k-1)\n   -- convention: arguments always ordered (S,P,mu) *)\ndegQ[SS_, PP_, mu_] := Table[(SS + PP + 3) - muhat[mu][[k]], {k, 4}]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* --- Gaudin ODE --- \n   Q'''' coefficient is\n   8(z-w1)^2(z-w2)^2 -- double singular points at the two Gaudin sites, as expected. C2,C4 are\n   the abstract Casimirs of the output irrep mu; S,P label the two input reps [S,S,0,0],[P,P,0,0]*)\nClearAll[gaudinODE];\ngaudinODE = (2*C2 + C2^2 - 2*C4 + 24*P + 2*C2*P + 20*P^2 + 4*P^3 + 24*S + 2*C2*S + 40*P*S + 12*P^2*S + 20*S^2 + 12*P*S^2 + 4*S^3)*Q[z]\n   + 4*(C2 - 4*P - 2*P^2 - 4*S - 4*P*S - 2*S^2)*(2*z + P*z + S*z - w1 - P*w1 - w2 - S*w2)*Derivative[1][Q][z]\n   - 4*(C2*z^2 - 6*P*z^2 - 4*P^2*z^2 - 6*S*z^2 - 8*P*S*z^2 - 4*S^2*z^2 - C2*z*w1 + 8*P*z*w1 + 6*P^2*z*w1 + 4*S*z*w1 + 8*P*S*z*w1\n      + 2*S^2*z*w1 - 2*P*w1^2 - 2*P^2*w1^2 - C2*z*w2 + 4*P*z*w2 + 2*P^2*z*w2 + 8*S*z*w2 + 8*P*S*z*w2 + 6*S^2*z*w2\n      + C2*w1*w2 - 4*P*w1*w2 - 2*P^2*w1*w2 - 4*S*w1*w2 - 8*P*S*w1*w2 - 2*S^2*w1*w2 - 2*S*w2^2 - 2*S^2*w2^2)*Derivative[2][Q][z]\n   - 16*(z - w1)*(z - w2)*(P*z + S*z - P*w1 - S*w2)*Derivative[3][Q][z]\n   + 8*(z - w1)^2*(z - w2)^2*Derivative[4][Q][z];\n(* punctures fixed at w1=0, w2=1 for this solver *)\nwsub = {w1 -> 0, w2 -> 1};",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* --- Gaudin ODE solver ---\n   Arguments always ordered (S,P,mu): S,P label the two input reps [S,S,0,0],[P,P,0,0]; mu is\n   the output irrep. Solves the 4th-order Gaudin ODE for the four polynomial Q's of degrees\n   degQ[S,P,mu], returned as monic coefficient lists (coeffs of z^0,z^1,...,z^m). GAUGE FIXING:\n   the four Q-degrees are strictly increasing, so any lower-degree solution can be added to a\n   higher one (q_k -> q_k + c q_j, j<k); removed by forcing the coefficient of z^(deg q_j) in\n   q_k to vanish for every j<k. *)\nClearAll[GaudinSolve];\nGaudinSolve[SS_, PP_, mu_] := Module[{ds, ode},\n   ds = degQ[SS, PP, mu];\n   ode = gaudinODE /. {C2 -> Cas2[mu], C4 -> Cas4[mu], S -> SS, P -> PP} /. wsub;\n   Table[Module[{m = ds[[kk]], gauge = ds[[1 ;; kk - 1]], q, cl, sol},\n       q = Sum[cq[j] z^j, {j, 0, m}];\n       cl = CoefficientList[Expand[ode /. Q -> Function[x, q /. z -> x]], z];\n       sol = Solve[Join[Thread[cl == 0], {cq[m] == 1}, Thread[(cq /@ gauge) == 0]], Table[cq[j], {j, 0, m}]];\n       Table[cq[j], {j, 0, m}] /. sol[[1]]], {kk, 4}]];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* example: (S,P)=(1,1), mu={2,1,1,0} *)\nGaudinSolve[1, 1, {2, 1, 1, 0}]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"342128\" data-output-id=\"73\" data-out-n=\"150\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"7\" data-sub-start=\"1\" data-sub-end=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[150]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrudzw5r-sfhwyyh\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1xsZWZ0XHsxXHJpZ2h0XH0sXGxlZnRcezAsLTEsMVxyaWdodFx9LFxsZWZ0XHswLDAsMCwxXHJpZ2h0XH0sXGxlZnRcezAsMCwwLDAsLVxmcmFjezV9ezJ9LDFccmlnaHRcfVxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.4em;vertical-align:-0.95em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">{</span></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">5</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">}</span></span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[150]= \\left\\{\\left\\{1\\right\\},\\left\\{0,-1,1\\right\\},\\left\\{0,0,0,1\\right\\},\\left\\{0,0,0,0,-\\frac{5}{2},1\\right\\}\\right\\}",
