  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* --- validation: every gauge-fixed Q_k solves the Gaudin ODE exactly, across full (S,P)\n   decompositions. Works directly off GaudinSolve's coefficient lists (BuildQs is just a display\n   convenience, not used for verification). NB: q is rebuilt as a Sum (SetDelayed) rather than a\n   Dot[coeffs, z^Range[...]] pure Function -- the latter has a degenerate edge case when\n   differentiating symbolically for length-1 coefficient lists (the deg=0 case) that spuriously\n   fails. Argument convention: (S,P,mu). *)\nClearAll[verifyGaudin];\nverifyGaudin[SS_, PP_, mu_] := Module[{qs, ds, ode, qf},\n   ds = degQ[SS, PP, mu]; qs = GaudinSolve[SS, PP, mu];\n   ode = gaudinODE /. {C2 -> Cas2[mu], C4 -> Cas4[mu], S -> SS, P -> PP} /. wsub;\n   AllTrue[Range[4], Module[{m = ds[[#]], cf = qs[[#]]},\n      qf[x_] := Sum[cf[[j + 1]] x^j, {j, 0, m}];\n      Expand[ode /. Q -> qf] === 0] &]];\nGrid[Table[{{SS, PP}, Length[irreps[SS, PP]], AllTrue[irreps[SS, PP], verifyGaudin[SS, PP, #] &]},\n   {SS, {1, 2, 3}}, {PP, {1, 2, 3}}] // Flatten[#, 1] &, Frame -> All]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"342128\" data-output-id=\"75\" data-out-n=\"156\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"10\" data-sub-start=\"13\" data-sub-end=\"14\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[156]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrudzxoc-gknzvm6\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:10.84em;vertical-align:-5.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:5.69em;\"><span style=\"top:-7.65em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"mtable\"><span class=\"vertical-separator\" style=\"height:10.8em;border-right-width:0.04em;border-right-style:solid;margin:0 -0.02em;vertical-align:-5.15em;\"></span><span class=\"arraycolsep\" style=\"width:0.5em;\"></span><span class=\"col-align-c\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:5.65em;\"><span style=\"top:-7.81em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-6.61em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class