 style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-4.9em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-6.1em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-7.3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-8.5em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-9.7em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-10.9em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-12.1em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-13.3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:7.65em;\"></span><span class=\"hline\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:5.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
